videos.headline: Early celebration costs New Mexico a TD
videos.description: New Mexico RB Bryson Carroll has a clear path to the end zone, but drops the ball at the one-yard line to negate the potential touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF_One-Play (Early celebration costs New Mexico a TD) 2019/10/11

videos.headline: Kinsey rumbles into end zone for 2nd TD
videos.description: Colorado State RB Marvin Kinsey Jr. finds pay dirt for the second time in the game, scoring from three yards out to give the Rams a 28-14 lead.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF One-Play (Kinsey rumbles into end zone for 2nd TD) 2019/10/11
